OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fclearing during Friday evening.
OL,7,FOvernight, a mixture of clear spells
OL,8,Fand cloud, some of this lingering over
OL,9,Fhills and near coasts to make it
OL,10,Fslightly murky with drizzle in places.
OL,11,FNot too chilly, but relatively cool in
OL,12,Frural areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FRather cloudy on Saturday,
OL,15,Fthe cloud bringing morning drizzle
OL,16,Fover the hills before lifting to keep
OL,17,Fit drier in the afternoon.
OL,18,FTemperatures slightly down on recently
OL,19,Fbut still rather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
